[02:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'processes. If you run into any errors with this&nbsp; node, try setting the autotune to false first. If&nbsp;&nbsp; that does not help, you may want to bypass it for&nbsp; now, as it is still very new. Then here we load&nbsp;&nbsp; the LoRA\'s. I am still using the CONSIS LoRA,&nbsp; which I have already added to the red note. &nbsp;'

[02:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'If you want to stack an \'F2K uncensored\' or&nbsp; any other LoRA, you can place it here. And&nbsp;&nbsp; here we load our \'refcontrol depth\' LoRA. As for&nbsp; below here, these are the split files loaders,&nbsp;&nbsp; un-bypass or un-mute the nodes to use them.&nbsp; Also, hook the loader nodes you want to use&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[02:30] [scene:talk]
